content:
First ingredients
• Beef Ramen 
• Diritos
• 1 square of cheese 
• Beef Jerky (Specifically Jack Link's)

Instructions 
•If in microwave, cook for 3 minutes in the microwave, if on stove, cook for 3 minutes while stirring the Ramen every 1 minute

•After the Ramen is done, grab your Beef jerky and cut it into small slices, after cutting it into small slices, you put the jerly right into your bowl of ramen 

•Then grab your cheese, slap it onto your Ramen, and then put a plate (any plate) on top of your bowl of Ramen, let it sit for 30 seconds

•After the Ramen is done sitting, take off the plate and stir the Ramen

•After stirring, grab your doritos and crush them, after crushing them, put them right into your Ramen.
